of what people do
with their food.

32:57.059 --> 32:58.925
A lot of people
smoke stuff for flavor.

32:58.927 --> 33:01.662
I smoke stuff for necessity.

33:01.664 --> 33:03.997
The flavor's
just an added bonus.

33:03.999 --> 33:06.133
So, this is kind of
the strips right here.

33:06.135 --> 33:08.201
This is what, what I'm after.

33:08.203 --> 33:10.404
Just kind of put it
into a quick brine.

33:10.406 --> 33:12.405
Really nice, beautiful,
thin strips.

33:12.407 --> 33:15.809
Very vibrant red,
very healthy fish.

33:15.811 --> 33:18.678
It's getting late,
creeping up to midnight.

33:18.680 --> 33:22.683
But I got the sun still out,
I can still see.

33:22.685 --> 33:25.485
There's no reason why
I wouldn't stick, stick it out.

33:25.487 --> 33:28.822
Just keep processing,
keep working.

33:28.824 --> 33:30.090
Winter's coming around soon,

33:30.092 --> 33:33.226
and I'll be leaving here
