the smokehouse of oxygen.

34:03.992 --> 34:05.792
♪ ♪

34:05.794 --> 34:11.131
♪ ♪

34:11.133 --> 34:14.667
And then I'm gonna make
a little airflow here,

34:14.669 --> 34:16.136
and then it can
breathe out the top.

34:16.138 --> 34:17.270
And that's kind of
what I want to see,

34:17.272 --> 34:20.473
is the smoke just
kind of pillowing out

34:20.475 --> 34:22.942
real slow, real smooth.

34:22.944 --> 34:27.681
That means that the fire's
burning slow and low.

34:27.683 --> 34:29.483
Awesome.

34:29.485 --> 34:31.418
Keep processing fish.

34:31.420 --> 34:37.824
♪ ♪

