35:44.893 --> 35:46.159
CHRIS: It's pretty.

35:46.161 --> 35:48.094
JESSI: All right.

35:48.096 --> 35:50.230
Thank you, fish,
thank you for your life.

35:50.232 --> 35:52.632
We've never seen anything
the likes of you before.

35:52.634 --> 35:54.301
Look at that.
All right, ready?

35:54.303 --> 35:55.301
CHRIS: Yeah.

35:55.303 --> 35:56.703
JESSI: God,
that's a gorgeous fish.

35:56.705 --> 35:57.504
CHRIS: Let's put him
out of his misery.

