37:48.283 --> 37:49.950
I think, over there.

37:49.952 --> 37:54.154
♪ ♪

37:54.156 --> 37:56.089
At least that sounds right.

37:56.091 --> 37:58.291
♪ ♪

37:58.293 --> 38:03.229
♪ ♪

38:03.231 --> 38:07.500
Spatial awareness,
