out across that flat.

39:43.732 --> 39:46.466
A lot of square miles.

39:46.468 --> 39:47.467
I'm excited.

39:47.469 --> 39:50.403
The kids put in a lot of work,
um, last year,

39:50.405 --> 39:52.872
and, hey, they put a lot
of work into this build.

39:52.874 --> 39:54.941
I'm really proud of them
